    "name": "BadSmith",
    "steam_appid": 2152830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152830/extras/36798f837a41be235a35845d8bb31fbd.avif?t=1732005323\" width=616 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BadSmith</strong> is a blacksmith simulator game about work, sweat and the burden of being in a fantasy world with all creatures. You play as a young blacksmith who looks after the forge of his father, who disappeared and no one knows where he is now.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152830/extras/4da4d802b6ac9c675764c414160237a0.poster.avif?t=1732005323\" width=616 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152830/extras/4da4d802b6ac9c675764c414160237a0.webm?t=1732005323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152830/extras/4da4d802b6ac9c675764c414160237a0.mp4?t=1732005323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152830/extras/31974c8112f9a86a55cf6821853b2473.avif?t=1732005323\" width=579 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main gameplay will be based on crafting unique items for heroes who go on raids to hunt monsters. At the same time, you must find out where our heroes are going and what requirements they have. If you make a sword unsuitable characteristics, it can break at a crucial moment or a hero can even die in the hands of a monster, leaving us only a skull and bones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152830/extras/ad91c48c01455799f08c1748aa18bed9.poster.avif?t=1732005323\" width=618 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152830/extras/ad91c48c01455799f08c1748aa18bed9.webm?t=1732005323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Work as a blacksmith in the forge</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Craft for customers a legendary weapon and armor</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build the full set for the heroes</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose your own path in this story with the customers</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover the Kingdom of Everton</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152830/extras/655c5c992efec7dd44786f7659739c69.poster.avif?t=1732005323\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152830/extras/655c5c992efec7dd44786f7659739c69.webm?t=1732005323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152830/extras/3bfdc35d37bd5a7ccbcca9194f1cdc0b.avif?t=1732005323\" width=579 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152830/extras/c289580336531693de0d001667c4b9ee.avif?t=1732005323\" width=616 height=136 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There will be <strong>3</strong> factions - <strong>Royal Guardians</strong>, <strong>Marauders</strong> and the <strong>Cultists</strong>. You can help one of the factions win the civil war, or even sell weapons to everyone and drown in orders and lack of time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152830/extras/4e9cf9b4b8463293187bf610c7c6de71.poster.avif?t=1732005323\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152830/extras/4e9cf9b4b8463293187bf610c7c6de71.webm?t=1732005323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152830/extras/4e9cf9b4b8463293187bf610c7c6de71.mp4?t=1732005323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our customers are heroes, citizens, wizards and not only them. Each client has their own order and story, which you can influence when creating a weapon or armory. The kingdom in which we will live and work is on the brink of civil war. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
